longBusinessSummary: Elcora Advanced Materials Corp., a graphite and graphene company, mines, processes, and refines graphite and graphene. It produces graphene and end graphene applications, as well as engages in the research and development activities. The company was formerly known as Elcora Resources Corp. and changed its name to Elcora Advanced Materials Corp. in February 2016. Elcora Advanced Materials Corp. was founded in 2011 and is headquartered in Bedford, Canada.
